# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Customer Retention Reasoning Agent — Environment Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your GitHub token.
# The agent works WITHOUT a token (rule-based fallback mode).
# Adding a token enables LLM-powered reasoning for richer strategies.
#
# NEVER commit the actual .env file to version control.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# GitHub Personal Access Token (enables LLM-backed reasoning via GitHub Models)
# Generate a token from: https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here
